author: Just Jared
title: Zayn Malik Films Cameo in 'Ocean's Eight' While in NYC
text:
Zayn Malik rocks a tie-dye hoodie as he steps out on Tuesday night (January 17) in New York City.
The 24-year-old musician trimmed up his beard a bit as he got ready to film a cameo in the upcoming Ocean’s Eight film.
PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Zayn Malik 
Also spotted out and about that night was Zayn ‘s girlfriend Gigi Hadid who stayed warm in a faux fur coat as she stepped out.
Also pictured inside: Gigi making her way to her apartment on Monday afternoon (January 16).
